## 15. Data Migration Plan

If the school has old records, migration should be handled carefully.

### Steps

- Collect existing spreadsheets and paper formats
- Clean duplicate records
- Map columns to the new schema
- Import in stages
- Validate imported records
- Keep an error log for unresolved rows

## 16. Risk Management

### Risks

- Requirements may change during development
- Old data may be inconsistent
- Some modules may need special hardware integration
- SMS or biometric devices may require extra setup
- Finance and grading logic may be politically sensitive in real use

### Mitigation

- Keep the design modular
- Add validation everywhere
- Build a staged rollout
- Use feature flags for uncertain features
- Confirm business rules before coding complex logic

